layers.text: Driver Francisco Torres. Driver of Vehicle 1 was on Bushwick Ave, turning onto Gates Ave, when he grazed the side of an unoccupied white Escalade, damaging the front and left side of the truck. Driver of Vehicle 1 said he panicked and took off.\n\nThe Escalade was parked on the side of the street with the church. Driver of Vehicle accident witnesses on the street, as well as people photographing his license plate.
